          <dt>Valve</dt><dd>Mitral</dd>
          <dt>Disease</dt><dd>Primary mitral regurgitation (high risk)</dd>
          <dt>Procedure</dt><dd>TEER</dd>
          <dt>Sample</dt><dd>78 (HRS publication)</dd>
          <dt>Follow-up</dt><dd>1 and 5 years</dd>
        </dl>
      </div>
      <div class="qf"><h4>Guidelines</h4>
        <p class="lab">ACC / AHA</p><p>Supported prohibitive-risk primary-MR TEER.</p>
        <p class="lab">ESC / EACTS</p><p>Supportive for inoperable primary MR.</p>
