        <p class="lab">ACC / AHA</p><p>Class 2a for TEER in appropriately selected secondary MR (2020 ACC/AHA).</p>
        <p class="lab">ESC / EACTS</p><p>Supports TEER in selected secondary MR (2021 ESC/EACTS).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="qf"><h4>FDA / regulatory</h4><p>Basis for FDA MitraClip expansion to secondary MR (2019).</p></div>
      <div class="qf"><h4>Timeline</h4><ul class='bul'><li>Enrollment: 2012–2017</li><li>Published: NEJM 2018 (TCT 2018)</li><li>5-year: NEJM 2023</li></ul></div>
