        <p class="lab">ACC / AHA</p><p>Defines the selection caveats around secondary-MR TEER.</p>
        <p class="lab">ESC / EACTS</p><p>Informs restrictive selection in secondary MR.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="qf"><h4>FDA / regulatory</h4><p>No expansion; shaped selection criteria.</p></div>
      <div class="qf"><h4>Timeline</h4><ul class='bul'><li>Enrollment: 2013–2017</li><li>Published: NEJM 2018</li><li>2-year follow-up: 2019</li></ul></div>
